</h3><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-77_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Another pillar of Business intelligence is strategic thinking and problem-solving. This goes beyond the ability to analyse data or excel in logical reasoning. It's about seeing the bigger picture, anticipating market trends, and devising innovative solutions to complex problems. It's the kind of intelligence that enables a leader to steer a company through tumultuous economic waters or to seize a market opportunity that others might miss.
