</h3><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-117_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In today's interconnected world, Goleman's concept of distributed intelligence is particularly relevant. Knowledge and skills needed in business are increasingly spread across networks and technological tools. This shifts the focus from individual knowledge hoarding to collaborative intelligence, leveraging the collective expertise of networks and systems.
